Class Counter.Partial

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.prometheus.client.metrics.Metric.Partial
      • io.prometheus.client.metrics.Counter.Partial
  • Enclosing class:
    Counter

    public class Counter.Partial
extends Metric.Partial

    A derivative of Counter that lets you accumulate labels to build a concrete metric via apply() for mutation with the methods of Counter.Child.
